Yes, the Imperium knows about these chips in 1120.  After all, the
SDG-313F strain of chips, a "lobotomized" version of the Cymbeline
chips, was introduced as the basis for Imperial transponders in 1088
(ibid, pages 70-71).  Further, since Admiral Stearns ordered the
