Intelligence, the possibility of Virus was recognized no later than
1108.  Finally, Dr. Arnold Rushorin, formerly of the Free University of
Aquitaine, defected to the Imperium in 1110, and published a
heavily-censored paper on the Cymbeline chips in 1114 (ibid, page 72).

