playing the game of nations (eg during the cold war) but by and large its
still a pretty good thing. This in turn influences how it behaves to others
and it is more inclined to \'go into bat\' for the little people now, more
than ever with the demise of the cold war as they don\'t have to worry about
encroaching on Russia\'s sphere of influence.

