Cool.  The original point was total destruction of "...all life on earth
...".  Societies ?  Sure.  All life ?  Not a hope in Hades.  Nature has
tried several times and failed.  Nothing we\'ve done up until now can
duplicate the power of nature.  Nothing, zip, zilch, diddly-squat.  The
power of St Helens was, what, about 4MT ?  And that affected such a small
area of the surface of the Earth as to laughable.  In 1000 years time,
