> Several things:
> Terrorist Attacks: High yield, small package, easy to smuggle that way.

Ah yes, of course, should have thought of that one.

> Infrastructure destruction

Hmm, this is a posibility if you\'re not worried about the side-effects, the
target is not hardened, and don\'t care if you take out everythng around the
target as well. In recent wars it has been shown that precision-guided
conventional munitions are much better for this purpose.

> EMP: Under traveller rules, most tech is subject to EMP even at TL 15

