can be proofed against EMP, assuming they want to pay for it, and how is EMP
going to effect laser or maser comms anyway? (unless the burst is in direct
line of sight for lasers)

Of course, if no-one uses nukes, maybe they didn\'t bother, but I suspect
spaceships are going to be EMP-proof by nature, given all the radiation they
have to put up with normally.

