There are 32 novels in the Dumarest of Terra series and they should be read
in the following order:

The Winds of Gath
Derai
Toyman
Kalin
The Jester at Scar
Lallia
Technos
Veruchia
Mayenne
Jondelle
Zenya
Eloise
Eye of the Zodiac
Jack of Swords
Spectrum of a Forgotten Sun
Haven of Darkness
Prison of Night
Incident on Ath
Quillian Sector
Web of Sand
Iduna\'s Universe
The Terra Data
World of Promise
Nectar of Heaven
The Terridae
The Coming Event
Earth is Heaven
Melome
Angado
Symbol of Terra
The Temple of Truth
The Return

Tubb originally intended for five other novels to be set on Earth after The
Return( although only recently published in the U.S., The Return was
written over a decade ago). Due to his advanced age, it is unlikely that
they will ever be written. I am currently hammering out a deal with Tubb\'s
agent to commission Tubb to write a 12,000 word novella set on Earth as a
follow up to "The Return" - keep your fingers crossed. Hopefully, if
written, this novella will at least tie up several of the loose ends that
still remain after Dumarest finds Earth at the end of The Return. 

Cordially,
Paul
