>Ah, good point!  And one I hadn\'t considered.  So, you could have
>Sensor 1, 2, 3 etc, representing the processing power needed to
>track multiple objects.  You could also have multiple programs for
>things, it takes Target to use turret weapons *and* Launch to
>control missiles or sand, and Gunner Interact to add the Gunner\'s
>skill to the task rolls.  You could have Sensor to *use* the sensors
>and Track 1, 2, to n to allow 1, 2..n objects to be tracked with
>those sensors.
>
>It also might be possible to have a multiplier for some of the
>programs based on the size of the ship.  Say, 50 x Size_Mod, so a
>Size 1 vessel needs a 50 CPU program, a Size 5 vessel needs a 250
>CPU version and a Size 9 vessel needs a 450 CPU version.
>
