    'body' => '>In mail you write:
>
>> I was fiddling around, trying to get decent acceleration for a GTL9 ship,
>> whne I realized that the GURPS Space light sails might work. Plugging the
>> numbers in (and assuming no silly mistakes on my part), I came up with a
